com.here.android.mpa.urbanmobility

Class NearbyCoverageResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.urbanmobility.NearbyCoverageResult

  • public class NearbyCoverageResult
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents information about nearby stops, lines, and city (in case if the user is assumed to be in one).

    IMPORTANT: Urban Mobility Coverage Search is a Beta feature. The related classes are subject to change without notice.
